source.dockerfile:
FROM pipeline:root
ADD ./app.binary /clonerefs
RUN umask 0002 && /clonerefs && find /go/src -type d -not -perm -0775 | xargs -r chmod g+xw
WORKDIR /go/src/github.com/openshift/installer/
ENV GOPATH=/go
RUN git submodule update --init

command:
#!/bin/sh
set -euo pipefail
trap 'kill $(jobs -p); exit 0' TERM

touch /tmp/done
echo "Waiting for artifacts to be extracted"
while true; do
	if [[ ! -f /tmp/done ]]; then
		echo "Artifacts extracted, will terminate after 30s"
		sleep 30
		echo "Exiting"
		exit 0
	fi
	sleep 5 & wait
done
containers.name: artifacts
